    "In addition, NetGPT will pose many challenges to the transmission, storage, computation, energy consumption, and other aspects of the network.",
    "Therefore, the approach of constructing a distributed learning architecture in a wireless network with limited multidimensional resources to promote training and inference of NetGPT must be evaluated, particularly in an effectively distributed manner.",
    "This may lead to more efficient distributed learning methods, which also require continued research efforts.",
    "To enable an AI agent with the perception, tool calling, and self-learning abilities and ensure the efficient communication between different AI agents, future networks will have to be improved such as by designing new architecture and protocol for AI agents.",
    "DTNs must be modeled in different scenarios."
